Class Landscape

java.lang.Object
  Landscape

public class Landscape
extends Object

Represents the landscape where all simulation objects live, work, and play.

Added new data fields to hold the bullet and defender (as SimObjects). Additionally the resources was changed from a SimObjectList to an ArrayList of SimObjectLists.
